twitch_info.title: Kamilia 3 - Stage 5 + M-Stage Speedrun in 2:16:07
twitch_info.description:
Wow, this run turned out pretty crazy. Cyber Area took less than 30 minutes, Influka Area was 2nd try, and M-Stage only took around 22 minutes.
Really happy with this time, don't plan on running this category again because it would be annoying to beat haha. One step closer to full game runs!
YouTube Upload: [http://youtu.be/pyraHBrfqdo](http://youtu.be/pyraHBrfqdo)
